in forgiveness."

01:52.166 --> 01:55.900
Now, you might rank bungee jumps
off a bridge in New Zealand

01:55.900 --> 01:58.333
or bachelor parties in Vegas
a few notches higher

01:58.333 --> 01:59.967
on the adventure ladder,

01:59.967 --> 02:02.400
