a victim who refuses to forgive.

02:08.633 --> 02:10.400
Think about the rewards.

02:10.400 --> 02:12.867
A chance to heal
those nasty wounds,

02:12.867 --> 02:15.300
reconcile with someone you love.

02:15.300 --> 02:17.567
