07:40.400 --> 07:43.433
Forgiveness is good
for your health.

07:48.800 --> 07:51.266
- Everybody's attention, please.

07:51.266 --> 07:54.367
Can I have your attention,
please?

07:54.367 --> 07:56.900
When Augustus Hill died,

07:56.900 --> 07:59.734
we thought we lost him forever,
but we didn't.

07:59.734 --> 08:02.367
He wrote a book

08:02.367 --> 08:04.934
about his life here,

08:04.934 --> 08:07.300
about your lives,

08:07.300 --> 08:10.700
