in their triumph.

08:36.367 --> 08:38.333
- Here you go.

09:17.533 --> 09:19.133
- Fuck, man.

09:19.133 --> 09:20.734
All right, already.

09:20.734 --> 09:21.967
Yo, quit fuckin' with me!

09:21.967 --> 09:23.934
- Rawls, Rawls! Take it easy.

09:23.934 --> 09:25.767
