or humiliate Burr Redding?

10:30.433 --> 10:33.200
- Prisoner number 01R934,

10:33.200 --> 10:35.233
Reginald Rawls.

10:45.300 --> 10:47.667
Convicted January 10, 2001,

10:47.667 --> 10:49.000
aggravated assault.

10:49.000 --> 10:51.233
Sentence: 12 years,

10:51.233 --> 10:54.367
