and I got 16.

42:52.000 --> 42:54.967
- Maybe it's your turn
to get to the point.

42:54.967 --> 43:00.700
- None of my children do drugs,
sell drugs, or hang in gangs.

43:00.700 --> 43:02.967
Each lives a life
of their own choosing,

43:02.967 --> 43:06.433
