to make a better world.

43:06.433 --> 43:09.467
My children are my pride

43:09.467 --> 43:13.834
because they make me proud.

43:13.834 --> 43:16.200
So, rather than use
this classroom

43:16.200 --> 43:20.633
as a place to plot your plans,

43:20.633 --> 43:24.133
use it for a real purpose,

43:24.133 --> 43:27.200
to learn.

43:27.200 --> 43:29.667
End of sermon.

43:29.667 --> 43:31.967
End of discussion.

43:39.467 --> 43:41.300
- Thanks.

43:44.100 --> 43:47.000
Hey, stranger, haven't seen
much of you lately.

43:47.000 --> 43:48.433
- Yeah, well, you know,
