43:57.200 --> 43:58.734
It's very sweet, very intimate.

43:58.734 --> 44:00.166
- Ryan, come on.
- What?

44:00.166 --> 44:02.066
You gonna tell me
I'm imagining it,

44:02.066 --> 44:03.867
that my eyes deceive me?
- No.

44:03.867 --> 44:05.500
- You asked me
to be nice to the guy.

44:05.500 --> 44:07.667
I tried, he blew me off.

44:07.667 --> 44:10.600
You know, I know you think
he's some sort of hotshot savior

44:10.600 --> 44:14.100
and all, but to me he's just
another fuckin' wanker.

44:14.100 --> 44:15.734
You two enjoy yourselves.

44:15.734 --> 44:18.667
Meanwhile, my little brother's
gonna die.

44:18.667 --> 44:20.734
- Ryan.
- What?

44:20.734 --> 44:24.633
- Promise me you won't
do anything to harm Jahfree.

44:24.633 --> 44:27.233
- Oh, gee, Ma,

44:27.233 --> 44:30.100
you really think I'm capable
of something like that?

44:38.600 --> 44:41.633
- Neema, I know we haven't had

44:41.633 --> 44:43.367
much of a chance to talk
since you arrived here--

44:43.367 --> 44:44.400
- That's probably because
we have

44:44.400 --> 44:46.433
nothing to say to each other.

44:46.433 --> 44:48.767
- Well, look, I know
on the outside you and me,

44:48.767 --> 44:50.200
we was never that friendly,
but--

44:50.200 --> 44:51.667
- Friendly?

44:51.667 --> 44:56.000
Redding, you are anathema to me.

44:56.000 --> 44:57.567
- See, there you go using
them big words,

44:57.567 --> 45:00.200
think you're going to curl me,
but it don't.

45:00.200 --> 45:02.166
- For the past
30-something years,

45:02.166 --> 45:04.300
