48:58.133 --> 49:01.433
bored with shaving,
brushing my teeth,

49:01.433 --> 49:04.100
taking a shit,
wiping my ass.

49:04.100 --> 49:05.900
- You know what?

49:05.900 --> 49:08.000
I don't think you're bored.

49:11.200 --> 49:14.633
I think you miss Tobias.

49:14.633 --> 49:18.266
- Well, he's turned
into a real firebrand.

49:18.266 --> 49:20.967
