52:07.934 --> 52:11.100
- I covered my tracks.

52:11.100 --> 52:12.433
- Shit.

52:12.433 --> 52:13.900
- Toby, look,
I'm telling you this--

52:13.900 --> 52:15.734
I'm telling you this...

52:19.266 --> 52:22.133
- I'm not bragging.
