54:01.667 --> 54:05.300
I got a tip for him,

54:05.300 --> 54:09.533
the sale
of illegal pharmaceuticals.

54:09.533 --> 54:12.633
- A man stands in the cemetery
reading a letter he wrote

54:12.633 --> 54:15.266
finally forgiving
his long-dead father.

54:15.266 --> 54:17.834
