of retaliation.

54:20.734 --> 54:23.734
Your boyfriend begs you
for one more chance,

54:23.734 --> 54:27.533
you say to a mirror
you're done hating yourself.

54:27.533 --> 54:29.633
But you know you're not.

54:29.633 --> 54:31.533
