forgive and remember.

54:33.667 --> 54:35.333
Remember that you might
wake up tomorrow

54:35.333 --> 54:37.600
and have to forgive
all over again,

54:37.600 --> 54:39.867
and again and again,

54:39.867 --> 54:42.800
the way the heart keeps beating
like a drum.

54:42.800 --> 54:44.100
Forgive.

54:44.100 --> 54:45.400
I can't.

54:45.400 --> 54:47.033
You can.

54:47.033 --> 54:50.233
Forgive. Forgive.

54:50.233 --> 54:51.700
I can't.

54:51.700 --> 54:55.000
You can.

54:55.000 --> 54:57.000
Forgive.

55:13.266 --> 55:18.100
- Same old story.

55:18.100 --> 55:20.633
I got fucked in the ass.

55:22.700 --> 55:24.600
- Sit down.

55:30.066 --> 55:32.000
Sit the fuck down.

55:34.467 --> 55:36.633
All right, guys,
welcome to Oz.

55:36.633 --> 55:38.700
Here's the procedure.
